      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows visible scratches and minor dents, with some inconsistency in the paint finish. The interior has worn upholstery and scuffed trim surfaces from regular use. Mechanically functional, but cosmetic wear is apparent throughout.",
      "price": 18500.0,
